snippet.title: Prison Chef’s Birthday Wish Comes True with a Surprise Burger #shorts
snippet.description: A prison chef dreamed of a tasty burger for his birthday, but the prison food was unbearable. Seeing his disappointment, his cellmate gathered ingredients from other inmates to surprise him. The chef prepared a delicious burger and even lit a simple candle. Just then, a guard arrived with a special "Happy Birthday" decoration. Overwhelmed with gratitude, the chef shared his burger with everyone, proving that kindness exists even behind bars.
